just a flak vest and a radio headset over his fancy suit and glorious dome.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1259\" height=\"840\" src=\"https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/law-and-order-organized-crime-season-5-episode-8-recap-headset.jpg?w=650\" alt=\"law-and-order-organized-crime-season-5-episode-8-recap\" srcset=\"https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/law-and-order-organized-crime-season-5-episode-8-recap-headset.jpg 1259w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/law-and-order-organized-crime-season-5-episode-8-recap-headset.jpg?resize=200,133 200w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/law-and-order-organized-crime-season-5-episode-8-recap-headset.jpg?resize=300,200 300w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/law-and-order-organized-crime-season-5-episode-8-recap-headset.jpg?resize=768,512 768w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/law-and-order-organized-crime-season-5-episode-8-recap-headset.jpg?resize=1024,683 1024w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/law-and-order-organized-crime-season-5-episode-8-recap-headset.jpg?resize=150,100 150w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/law-and-order-organized-crime-season-5-episode-8-recap-headset.jpg?resize=600,400 600w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/law-and-order-organized-crime-season-5-episode-8-recap-headset.jpg?resize=280,187 280w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/law-and-order-organized-crime-season-5-episode-8-recap-headset.jpg?resize=1000,667 1000w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/law-and-order-organized-crime-season-5-episode-8-recap-headset.jpg?resize=244,163 244w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/law-and-order-organized-crime-season-5-episode-8-recap-headset.jpg?resize=1160,774 1160w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/law-and-order-organized-crime-season-5-episode-8-recap-headset.jpg?resize=900,600 900w, https://tv